            p Whether you're outfitting your first kitchen or expanding your tool collection, you'll love this handy set. It includes nine of OXO's most essential everyday tools. To keep everything organized and within easy reach in the kitchen, the set also includes a sleek, space-saving utensil holder. All your essential kitchen tools will always be in quick reach with this product.
            .offset-top-20
              ul.list-inline
                li.text-middle Quantity:
